    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Estimation of gas price should only happen when i send a transaction, before you actually send it. So steps:\n1. i send using eth.sendTransaction(...) and don't provide a gas amount.\n2. you take that transaction and run it through the call/estiamteGas mechanism and get the used gas amount\n3. you use this estimate + 20 000 gas as default\n   4 .you send the actual transaction, which now uses up gas.\n",
